io.github.u004.steamid

Class SteamId

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.u004.steamid.SteamId

  • public final class SteamId
extends Object
    A Steam ID representation.

    SteamId is the class that represents Steam ID as an entity and includes a lot of methods to convert and parse to/from any Steam-like string.

    Since:
    0.1.0
